{"tid":1024691,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"應該冇人鼻敏感可以好似我咁嚴重","createTime":"2019-02-16T18:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T16:39:14.000Z","uid":184036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e88ed1f8c7b48ee2160ab52191c6c9fefdb588","tid":1024691,"uid":184036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"以前細細個都冇事<br />\n呢幾年就開始嚟料 鼻敏感愈嚟愈勁<br />\n啲鼻水不停流 冇停過咁濟<br />\n又會打乞嚏 鼻塞 塞到呼吸唔到<br />\n食過幾隻藥 得佳x天有用<br />\n但係而家食完都冇用 一係就一次過食兩粒（包裝寫1日1粒）<br />\n最誇張係半個鐘就用哂一包紙巾 張張都濕哂 成個鼻都因為係咁呻鼻涕好痛<br />\n發作時 鼻入面又唔知點解會間唔中吉吉地痛 個人又會好似發發地燒咁好慶<br />\n基本上 一鼻敏感全日都做唔到嘢 根本專心唔到 一定要長時間拎紙巾包住個鼻撳實個鼻先得<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571c10630af1f632f1a19f065d803fc9e8f18ee0","tid":1024691,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:08:55.000Z","msg":"一分鐘都用一包啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587434acb553a109efd01a927144e741a45bf349","tid":1024691,"uid":184036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"其實仲會發冷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一鼻敏感就算夏天30度我都要著長袖衫出街先夠暖"},{"pid":"9ad4382e092041d44164100a80996fccf73d2bf8","tid":1024691,"uid":111493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"我以前嚴重過你<br />\n咩都流鼻水<br />\n咩藥都抗左<br />\n帶埋眼腫埋敏感<br />\n最後做天炙幾年<br />\n夏天狂游水就好返8成啦"},{"pid":"ac75a2d066b9a33f3565f1beff4e660cb55deef2","tid":1024691,"uid":184537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"好撚普通 個個嚴重鼻敏感嘅人都係咁 唔好以為自己最慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69375a1928ec900dda82ec467caaa33b10fe378","tid":1024691,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"有噴鼻唔用 抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 以前嚴重過你 噴完好返冇鼻水"},{"pid":"21e06cba1973813375e0d8427084dc28a620f42c","tid":1024691,"uid":75356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"轉天氣嗰陣同你差唔多，做運動可以舒緩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12e8155b32fac72f789979c0c68976a95542366","tid":1024691,"uid":13865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T19:10:26.000Z","msg":"我嚴重過你<br />\n你試下用類固醇噴鼻<br />\n用完一排會好啲"},{"pid":"0966bc8b5cf720c2b19e3ece5110869c0fc40001","tid":1024691,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac75a2d066b9a33f3565f1beff4e660cb55deef2","tid":1024691,"uid":184537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"好撚普通 個個嚴重鼻敏感嘅人都係咁 唔好以為自己最慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T23:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪就係 根本就係鼻敏感嘅形容"},{"pid":"6d1d93648387768fb2c876162343ac08fd9b4904","tid":1024691,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T23:19:04.000Z","msg":"鼻入面有啲痛 不如去check下啦"},{"pid":"52c79f04ab131133046f97fffce719fc584ee23f","tid":1024691,"uid":115584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:59:51.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣嚴重 一日用一卷紙巾 一日打二百個乞痴<br />\n朝早起身凍親或者捽鼻就黎料 食咩藥都冇用 <br />\n屋企掃地搬屋送貨 索一索都黎料<br />\n但好係好喺每次瞓返8個鐘就完全冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a6b2ae551c9024eee965a50c61a1aeecb09c78","tid":1024691,"uid":11496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c79f04ab131133046f97fffce719fc584ee23f","tid":1024691,"uid":115584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:59:51.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣嚴重 一日用一卷紙巾 一日打二百個乞痴<br />\n朝早起身凍親或者捽鼻就黎料 食咩藥都冇用 <br />\n屋企掃地搬屋送貨 索一索都黎料<br />\n但好係好喺每次瞓返8個鐘就完全冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"我同你相反 每次訓醒覺（無論長短） 頭十分